showdown over President
Trump's executive order on
immigration.

09:57.130 --> 10:01.734 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
For the first of two looks at
what's at stake,
we are joined first by
Washington State Attorney

10:01.768 --> 10:04.270 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
General Bob Ferguson from
Seattle.

10:04.304 --> 10:09.609 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
It was his suit that led to this
weekend's
temporary shutdown of the ban.

10:09.642 --> 10:11.644 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Attorney General Ferguson,
thanks for joining
us.

10:11.678 --> 10:13.413 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
BOB FERGUSON, Washington State
Attorney General:
Thanks for having me on.

10:13.446 --> 10:18.585 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: If you -- if the
court lifts this
ban, lifts the temporary
restraining order,

10:18.618 --> 10:20.386 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
will you appeal to the Supreme
Court?

10:20.420 --> 10:25.592 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BOB FERGUSON: Well, to be
crystal clear, I
will use every tool I have to
make sure that

10:25.625 --> 10:29.095 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
this unconstitutional executive
order doesn't
stand.

10:29.128 --> 10:33.833 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
That said, we're confident the
Ninth Circuit
will affirm what Judge Robart,
who was appointed,

10:33.867 --> 10:37.904 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
of course, by President George
W. Bush, will
affirm his decision to grant
that TRO.

10:37.937 --> 10:43.276 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: I assume you're
anticipating if
he does keep it in place that
the Justice

10:43.309 --> 10:45.745 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Department will take it to the
Supreme Court.

10:45.778 --> 10:50.917 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
What's your sense of how your
chances would
fare on the current court?

10:50.950 --> 10:53.586 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
BOB FERGUSON: Well, I feel very
confident.

10:53.620 --> 10:58.625 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
As I mentioned, Judge Robart is
a very serious,
well-respected judge appointed
by President

10:58.658 --> 11:00.159 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
George W. Bush.

11:00.193 --> 11:05.164 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
