joins us from
Capitol Hill.

15:29.562 --> 15:31.764 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Mr. Yoho, thanks for being with
us.

15:31.798 --> 15:33.065 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
I don't know.

15:33.099 --> 15:34.534 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I hope you were able to hear the
attorney
general from Washington.

15:34.567 --> 15:35.535 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
REP.

15:35.568 --> 15:36.536 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
TED YOHO (R), Florida: Yes, I
was.

15:36.569 --> 15:37.537 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Yes.

15:37.570 --> 15:38.905 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JOHN YANG: What do you say to
him?

15:38.938 --> 15:40.006 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
He says this violates both the
Constitution
and immigration law.

15:40.039 --> 15:41.007 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
What do you say to that?

15:41.040 --> 15:42.008 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
REP.

15:42.041 --> 15:43.976 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
TED YOHO: I disagree with that.

15:44.010 --> 15:47.580 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
