executive, regardless
who it is, has the ability to
decide who comes

15:47.613 --> 15:50.416 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
in and doesn't if it's a
national security
risk.

15:50.449 --> 15:55.021 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
