come back
in 30 days, reassess it, 60, 90,
and 120 days.

16:06.232 --> 16:07.266 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
This is a pause.

16:07.300 --> 16:10.303 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
This is not a ban, complete ban.

16:10.336 --> 16:12.104 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
It is a pause.

16:12.138 --> 16:17.877 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I think anybody that is
concerned with
national security, and if you
look at our

16:17.910 --> 16:22.014 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Constitution -- he kept talking
about being
Constitution -- the Constitution
states very

16:22.048 --> 16:26.953 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
clearly that the number one task
of our government
is to provide for the common
defense and protection

16:26.986 --> 16:28.821 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
of this country.

16:28.855 --> 16:33.759 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I think, when you look
around the world,
other areas that have not done
this, I think

16:33.793 --> 16:37.663 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
they're wishing they would have
been a little
bit more stringent in the
examination of people

16:37.697 --> 16:39.532 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
coming in, in the refugee
program.

16:39.565 --> 16:44.070 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
You know, look at Belgium, look
at Paris,
look at Germany.

16:44.103 --> 16:47.807 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And I think this is a time that
we have to
do that.

16:47.840 --> 16:50.142 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And it's -- again, it's a
temporary pause.

16:50.176 --> 16:55.047 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And people, I think, just need
to calm down,
let us work through the process.

16:55.081 --> 16:56.816 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
The courts will work this out.

16:56.849 --> 17:01.220 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But I think it's also good that
it brought
to light how we have to fix our
immigration

17:01.254 --> 17:02.221 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
policy.

17:02.255 --> 17:04.023 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
So I welcome that, too.

17:04.056 --> 17:08.394 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: And the opponents of
this are also
arguing that -- in their court
challenge,

17:08.427 --> 17:13.833 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
that this creates -- even this
ban, this temporary
-- temporary pause, as you call
it, as you

17:13.866 --> 17:20.006 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
